oshi\'\'|to light a lamp, or lead a funeral procession}}\n|fr=Funécire|frmeaning=From \'\'{{tt|funéraire|funerary}}\'\' and \'\'{{tt|cire|wax}}\'\'\n|es=Litwick|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Lichtel|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Licht|light}}\'\' and \'\'{{tt|Wichtel|gnome}}\'\'\n|it=Litwick|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=불켜미 \'\'Bulkyeomi\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|불 \'\'bul\'\'|fire or light}}, {{tt|켜다 \'\'kyeoda\'\'|to turn on (usually light or fire)}}, and {{tt|~이 \'\'~i\'\'|diminutive suffix meaning \'one who does something\'}}; literally means "one who turns on the lights"\n|zh_cmn=燭光靈 / 烛光灵 \'\'Zhúguānglíng\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|燭光 \'\'zhúguāng\'\'|candle light}}, {{tt|靈 \'\'líng\'\'|spirit}}, and {{tt|幽靈 \'\'yōulíng\'\'|ghost, phantom}}\n|ru=Литвик \'\'Litvik\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n{{left clear}}\n<!--\n==Notes==\n<references />-->\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Ghost|type2=Fire}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Ghost|prevnum=606|prev=Beheeyem|nextnum=608|next=Lampent}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Lichtel]]\n[[es:Litwick]]\n[[fr:Funécire]]\n[[it:Litwick]]\n[[ja:ヒトモシ]]\n[[zh:烛光灵]]'}